{"tid":2089043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO一平權 連登仔第一反應就係走","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T18:17:57.000Z","uid":37959,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7804fc4f5d06cda120afb0de9df4ac683930fd78","tid":2089043,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"BNO未平權：<br />\n攬炒、推翻共產黨、港獨<br />\n<br />\nBNO一平權：<br />\nBye<br />\n<br />\n偏偏趕住走既係一班 平時自稱黃絲 日日食黃店、IG圍內po文宣刷光環 十次發夢九次推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係唔比你走 唔該一齊推翻共產黨先再諗走唔走<br />\n屎就一齊搞出黎 而家搞到一半就走 你點對得住冇得走既人<br />\n<br />\n除非你有高危人士 否則趕住走既都係仆街"},{"pid":"7a5e39548dab3984183761d8890c8c2d89abbf78","tid":2089043,"uid":109345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"我唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e821c9f77c76bb9ded72e9c390df5e3652fe778f","tid":2089043,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清"},{"pid":"63337701bcbcf998a4f688ec9a424fc8b3330d03","tid":2089043,"uid":181474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲人咁似琴日爭住del po嗰啲人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85615a8a86aafa8e850285af6037409995fd0417","tid":2089043,"uid":160363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7804fc4f5d06cda120afb0de9df4ac683930fd78","tid":2089043,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"BNO未平權：<br />\n攬炒、推翻共產黨、港獨<br />\n<br />\nBNO一平權：<br />\nBye<br />\n<br />\n偏偏趕住走既係一班 平時自稱黃絲 日日食黃店、IG圍內po文宣刷光環 十次發夢九次推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係唔比你走 唔該一齊推翻共產黨先再諗走唔走<br />\n屎就一齊搞出黎 而家搞到一半就走 你點對得住冇得走既人<br />\n<br />\n除非你有高危人士 否則趕住走既都係仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"根本好多香港人都係仆街仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi